I"#<p>Chris discovers he’s gay, Teagan writes poems about Ebola, Ariana falls in love with an older man, and much more. Recorded live at the Tranzac in Toronto.</p>

<p>Ariana’s poem in this episode was written at a point in her life when she was “really into slam poetry.” Her poem’s format was inspired by Kevin Kantor’s “Honest Confessions on Letting Go.”</p>

